title: 304. Andy & DJ CTI: FBI Arrests Peter Navarro, Global Elite Meeting & Ron DeSantis Vetoes $35M Tampa Bay Rays Complex
itunes:title: 304. Andy & DJ CTI: FBI Arrests Peter Navarro, Global Elite Meeting & Ron DeSantis Vetoes $35M Tampa Bay Rays Complex
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the arrest of Peter Navarro one day after he vowed to impeach President Biden, global elites meeting in Washington, DC for Bilderberg group meeting, and Ron DeSantis vetoing the $35M Tampa Bay Rays baseball complex after the team's gun control tweet.
